"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-olympics-2024-watch-tv-online-live-stream-b2577339.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The Independent's journalism is supported by our readers.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3077625341131338e-31, \"text\": \"The Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When you purchase through links on our site, we may earn commission.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 33rd Olympic Games begins on July 24, and will last until early August  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 525, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  The SummerOlympicsare upon us, with the biggest event of the sporting calendar underway inParis.\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Three years since the postponed Tokyo Olympics, the world's best athletes will descend on the French capital with hopes of taking home the most important medal in sport.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 680, \"end\": 694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999987423962, \"rank\": 1.2575479732108193e-09, \"text\": \"Tokyo Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 742, \"end\": 748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8908197923428393, \"rank\": 0.08146913993262477, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 33rd Olympic Games marks a return to Europe for the first time since London 2012, with Paris becoming one of three cities - along with the UK capital and Los Angeles - to have hosted the games three times.\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 892, \"end\": 903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999998228036177, \"rank\": 1.771951401853147e-07, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999994481641, \"rank\": 5.519484831858076e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9851986677116263, \"rank\": 0.011911630895125657, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 977, \"end\": 988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999948799274189, \"rank\": 3.4293236768509753e-06, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French capital last hosted the games 100 years ago, and all eyes will be on the City of Light once more as a new generation of athletes look to write their names in history.\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8908197923428393, \"rank\": 0.08146913993262477, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tickets for the games are still on sale on some platforms, but below we have all the information on how fans at home can watch the action.\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All of the action from Paris 2024 will be live on Eurosport and discovery+, the official home of the Olympics in the United Kingdom.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1466, \"end\": 1480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9827681258530063, \"rank\": 0.017534017806734855, \"text\": \"United Kingdom\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic_in_the_United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eurosport 1 and 2 will broadcast coverage on every day of the competition between 7am and 10.30pm, and customers can purchase Eurosport as part of a Sky, Virgin Media or TNT package on linear TV.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1677, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1631, \"end\": 1634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.9999992601786297, \"rank\": 7.025875037777458e-07, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 1652, \"end\": 1655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999999991528057, \"rank\": 7.894173925133454e-10, \"text\": \"TNT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1674, \"end\": 1676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television\", \"score\": 0.9589802566666583, \"rank\": 0.042774332862517896, \"text\": \"TV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+will be the streaming hub of the Olympics, with coverage spanning around 55 dedicated channels.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"New customers can sign up for just \\u00a33.99 per month as part of a special Olympics offer.\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC has also reached agreement to continue its coverage of the Games.\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1878, \"end\": 1881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"score\": 0.9569763517630253, \"rank\": 0.0444109365715776, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The broadcaster is limited to showing live action on one linear TV channel and one digital channel via the BBC iPlayer or BBC Sport website.\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 2088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2055, \"end\": 2058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"score\": 0.9569763517630253, \"rank\": 0.0444109365715776, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_News\"}, {\"begin\": 2059, \"end\": 2066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"iPlayer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\"}, {\"begin\": 2070, \"end\": 2079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9974674999368467, \"rank\": 0.0025389266721685616, \"text\": \"BBC Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TV coverage begins at 8am BST daily on BBC One and continues until the 10pm news, switching briefly to BBC Two during earlier news bulletins.\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2115, \"end\": 2118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.3497125488543554e-12, \"text\": \"BST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\"}, {\"begin\": 2128, \"end\": 2135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0903893581545795e-17, \"text\": \"BBC One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are travelling abroad and want to watch major sporting events, you might need a VPN to unblock your streaming app.\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our VPN round-up is here to help and includesdeals on VPNsin the market.\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Viewers using a VPN need to make sure that they comply with any local regulations where they are, and also with the terms of their service provider.\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2575, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games begin on 24 July with matches in the football and rugby sevens, though the 'official' start to the Olympics takes place on 26 July with the Opening Ceremony at 6.30pm BST.\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2758, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2727, \"end\": 2743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9416765842425093, \"rank\": 0.06180171954847291, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\"}, {\"begin\": 2754, \"end\": 2757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.3497125488543554e-12, \"text\": \"BST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the first time in history, the ceremony will not take place in a stadium, but rather along the banks of the Seine.\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2871, \"end\": 2876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999327042155, \"rank\": 6.668664029307922e-08, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is then daily action until 11 August, when the final events take place in several sports - including athletics and basketball - before the Closing Ceremony takes place in the Stade de France at 8pm BST.\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 3087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Independent vetsbetting sitesfor useability, security and responsible gambling tools.\", \"from\": 3089, \"to\": 3178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can claimfree betshere to use across a range of sports.\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please read the terms.\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3261, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We may earn commission from some of the links in this article, but we never allow this to influence our content.\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This revenue helps to fund journalism across The Independent.\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3490, \"end\": 3501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999999413376, \"rank\": 5.5532313765183405e-11, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"